What do all successful designers have in common?
The ability to approach complex challenges with simple, yet innovative solutions. 
And while we all have our own techniques for problem solving — from team brainstorming sessions to step-by-step formulas — sometimes we need to approach our work from an entirely different angle. 
Here, we’ve rounded up 11 inspirational design articles from creative thought leaders around the web.
Spanning everything from app interactions to modern web design monotony, these reads are sure to help you see age-old problems in a new light.
